OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 6 May to Fri 15 MayFA
OL,6,Ffairly quiet start to the period looks
OL,7,Flikely with many areas seeing a good
OL,8,Fdeal of dry weather. That said we are
OL,9,Funlikely to see a return of the
OL,10,Fcompletely dry and warm weather we
OL,11,Fhave see in recent days, with clear or
OL,12,Fsunny periods and showers more likely.
OL,13,FToward the latter part of the period a
OL,14,Ftrend toward more changeable weather
OL,15,Fis favoured although there should
OL,16,Fstill be some drier intervals. After a
OL,17,Fcold start to the period, especially
OL,18,Fin the north, temperatures likely
OL,19,Freturning close to average later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
